<item>
            <title>[LU-15739] LUTF doesn&apos;t show actual status of test suites</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15739</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;From the below link we can see that all tests show &quot;pass&quot;, but if click into each test, they actual failed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;summary shows pass&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/8c8f8733-eb07-4454-9d80-6f0c6af06fde&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/8c8f8733-eb07-4454-9d80-6f0c6af06fde&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;for example udsp actually failed&lt;/p&gt;

